</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FC8E653B876EB1341B9F5379FE57FA27" pageId="33" pageNumber="226" type="breeding">
<paragraph id="B42B36B0876EB1341B9F5379FE57FA27" blockId="33.[196,1405,721,1972]" pageId="33" pageNumber="226">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA2876EB1341B9F5379FED8FA71" bold="true" box="[198,332,1387,1420]" pageId="33" pageNumber="226">Breeding.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but age of specimens implies that breeding occurs during several months of the year, with peaks in winter and spring.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FC8E653B876EB1341B9D53F3FBFAF9FF" box="[196,1134,1505,1538]" pageId="33" pageNumber="226" type="activity">
